reviewText: The song was nothing like I had imagined or how I read chicka chicka boom boom! In fact the video for the boom boom was pretty awful. I still love the book but disappointed with the videos.
Keeps my kids engaged the entire time.

Daughter loves reading this book on her own!!
Great price and came in great shape!!
Great Book for Children to learn the numbers and sing when doing so!!
Colorful Book!!

I got this video for kindergarteners, but my grandchildren love it too!  It's just not quite as good as Chicka Chicka Boom Boom!
Very helpful learner though.  Kids pick up on the counting with the help of this book.

a good video to backup you kids in numbers.if they know how to count 1 to 10 then this video can help improved their counting to a hundred with easy to understand words used. my kid like it very much. she watch it every day.
My 4 yr. old grandchildren love this DVD. Not only is it entertaining, but educational. Just as with the Chicka Chicka Boom Boom, the music & performer are very good.
